com.mycompany.pewpewgame.controllers

Class GameController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mycompany.pewpewgame.controllers.GameController

  • public class GameController
extends Object
    This is the master controller of the game logic. It uses subcontrollers and object methods to complete most of its tasks. rendering is done using the Renderer class.
